\section{Projects}  

\textbf{Real Estate Analytics Platform:}  
End-to-end ELT pipeline processing Redfin data. Extracted data to AWS S3, transformed via Python, loaded to Snowflake with Snowpipe, and visualized in Power BI using optimized DAX and semantic models. Emphasis on business metric definition and performance tuning.  
\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/StreamAnalysis}{[GitHub]}

\textbf{Power BI KPI Dashboard:}  
Designed and deployed a sales analysis dashboard in Power BI; standardized KPIs and optimized queries, reducing processing time by 20\%. Integrated custom DAX measures and documentation to enable self-service.  
\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/SalesReport}{[GitHub]}

\textbf{Weather API Pipeline:}  
ETL pipeline fetching weather data, transforming it with Pandas, storing in Snowflake, and reporting via Power BI. Illustrated metric governance and documentation best practices.  
\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/StreamAnalysis}{[GitHub]}

\textbf{Sentiment Analysis Pipeline:}  
Automated social media sentiment analysis using BeautifulSoup, Selenium, and Scikit-learn. Highlighted automation, text mining, and Python proficiency.  
\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/Twitter-Sentiment-Analysis}{[GitHub]}

